query: SELECT DISTINCT team, COUNT(*) as player_count FROM players WHERE team NOT IN ('Hawks', 'Celtics', 'Nets', 'Hornets', 'Bulls', 'Cavaliers', 'Mavericks', 'Nuggets', 'Pistons', 'Warriors', 'Rockets', 'Pacers', 'Clippers', 'Lakers', 'Grizzlies', 'Heat', 'Bucks', 'Timberwolves', 'Pelicans', 'Knicks', 'Thunder', 'Magic', 'Sixers', 'Suns', 'Trail Blazers', 'Kings', 'Spurs', 'Raptors', 'Jazz', 'Wizards') AND team IS NOT NULL GROUP BY team ORDER BY team;
